{"title":"mybatis转义字符","date":"2019-08-24T09:47:02.000Z","link":"post/mybatis转义字符","tags":["mybatis"],"categories":["技术"],"updated":"2019-09-03T10:05:10.272Z","content":"<p>报错：  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>org.apache.ibatis.builder.BuilderException: Error creating document instance.  Cause: org.xml.sax.SAXParseException: The content of elements must consist of well-formed character data or markup.  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>产生原因是因为在mybatis的sql语句中使用了小于号（‘&lt;’）<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p>在sql语句中，不能直接用大于号、小于号等字符，应使用转义字符来替代  </p>\n<div class=\"article-bounded\"><div class=\"article-table\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>转义字符</th>\n<th>原符号</th>\n<th>含义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>&amp;gt;</td>\n<td>&gt;</td>\n<td>小于号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;lt;</td>\n<td>&lt;</td>\n<td>大于号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;amp;</td>\n<td>&amp;</td>\n<td>和</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;apos;</td>\n<td>‘</td>\n<td>单引号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;quot;</td>\n<td>“</td>\n<td>双引号</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>\n<p>示例：  </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">转义前：SELECT * FROM test WHERE 1 = 1 AND start_date &lt;= CURRENT_DATE AND end_date &gt;= CURRENT_DATE </span><br><span class=\"line\">转义后：SELECT * FROM test WHERE 1 = 1 AND start_date  &amp;lt;= CURRENT_DATE AND end_date &amp;gt;= CURRENT_DATE</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"最近有点丧","link":"post/最近有点丧"},"next":{"title":"第一次坐飞机","link":"post/第一次坐飞机"},"plink":"https://uoylive.github.io/post/mybatis转义字符/"}